{"tid":2417775,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白衣人暴動案今開審  莊榮輝兩認疑犯無下文 警篩走7.21證人","createTime":"2021-02-22T06:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T07:00:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f590f3cc20c1e56e7e9ca210bb26c555a2beb449","tid":2417775,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/IKWRPA6RJ5ATHGNZTFDPE4T7WM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FIKWRPA6RJ5ATHGNZTFDPE4T7WM%2F&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYzr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=38147c08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FIKWRPA6RJ5ATHGNZTFDPE4T7WM%2F&h=5a21c9cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/IKWRPA6RJ5ATHGNZTFDPE4T7WM/</a><br />\n<br />\n白衣人暴動案今開審 <br />\n莊榮輝兩認疑犯無下文 警篩走7.21證人<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】元朗7.21白衣人暴動案今日開審。曾被警方形容為「非常重要證人」、前年認人程序認出兩名疑犯的民主黨中委莊榮輝，卻被篩出證人名單，不獲安排上庭作供。由原告變被告的民主黨副主席林卓廷，同樣被排除出庭作供及認人，他批評，警方對涉及民主陣營人士案件以雷霆萬鈞態度處理，對白衫兇徒則放軟手腳，莊榮輝則形容自己如同乞求出庭，質疑警方欲放生疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：有證人憂起底 申匿名被拒<br />\n<br />\n前年7.21元朗站發生白衣人無差別襲擊市民事件，時任立法會議員林卓廷及莊榮輝都有到場視察，事後曾協助警方調查。白衣人案件開審前夕，兩人一同召開記者會，指前年協助認出疑犯的莊榮輝未獲邀出庭作證，當日在場的另一黨友冼卓嵐則獲邀出庭作供，及再次參與認人手續，惟冼未能再認出疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Y78F9Qwb_r-W6GDUpGKrjua-j_Y=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UMWRH4UWQZE5BEQJNNJUX2OM3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FY78F9Qwb_r-W6GDUpGKrjua-j_Y%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUMWRH4UWQZE5BEQJNNJUX2OM3I.jpg&h=17d11507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民主黨林卓廷（左）及莊榮輝昨開記招，播出二人月初兩度致電警方查問上庭安排的片段。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警辯稱疑犯認罪 莊：似乞求出庭<br />\n<br />\n記者會播出莊榮輝月初兩度致電警方查問因由的片段，在電話通話中警方解釋莊榮輝所指的疑犯已認罪，證據充足，故未安排他上庭，又稱有其他證人證供與莊的口供有相同資料。莊質疑，疑犯或在庭上反口不認罪，警方則指屆時律政司有可能再要求莊出庭作證。莊榮輝形容自己如同乞求出庭，質疑警方欲放生疑犯，對警隊處理案件的手法感到失望及痛心。<br />\n<br />\n曾任廉署調查主任的林卓廷亦指，........................<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷質疑向莊榮輝解釋的警員的說法貽笑大方，...................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷：警查白衣人如軟腳蟹<br />\n<br />\n林直斥警方調查7.21白衫人的方式如同軟腳蟹，質疑與7.21恐襲當晚帶隊到南邊圍村搜查及其後調任新界北總區刑事總部警司游乃強負責調查7.21事件的重案組有關，直言依靠警方刑事調查，尋找7.21真相恐遙遙無期，質疑警方有企圖掩飾及包庇。<br />\n<br />\n法政匯思成員、大律師蘇俊文認為，.........................<br />\n<br />\n對林卓廷及莊榮輝未獲安排為證人，......................<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/K0fXcV31OVN6gdVGh102vR6WSEQ=/2036x1148/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4Y54F6PZ6BDARI55ACSIOADPBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FK0fXcV31OVN6gdVGh102vR6WSEQ%3D%2F2036x1148%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4Y54F6PZ6BDARI55ACSIOADPBM.jpg&h=ed76a9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■7.21當晚有防暴警與持棍白衣人拍膊交談，被轟勾結。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bF7_tKZD0-axL7G03AuV45QY6i0=/2452x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GUYXSJVOOZCEXFJUQY6ABAR4WA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbF7_tKZD0-axL7G03AuV45QY6i0%3D%2F2452x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGUYXSJVOOZCEXFJUQY6ABAR4WA.jpg&h=b830ff18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冼卓嵐"},{"pid":"e6df4b9a7ebd665c77ea2a1a8cae843a7838e1ce","tid":2417775,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:50:25.000Z","msg":"Over my dead body <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86eedb9648d832848184e95b4b3b0fdb521eaa37","tid":2417775,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:00:47.000Z","msg":"最後話由於無證人，唯有撒控<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}